###Final Meal

Easy! Everything is done and now all that's left is to eat it.
I seasoned with salt and pepper.
Not bad for essentially being weeds growing in the back yard.
The taste reminded me of asparagus but not quite as strong.
I threw in some cashews and sesame seeds to the stir fry last minute to add to the texture.

